import * as React from "react";
import {
  TextField,
  FormControl,
  InputLabel,
  Select,
  FormLabel,
  RadioGroup,
  MenuItem,
  FormControlLabel,
  Radio,
} from "@mui/material";
import { citizenship, status, channels } from "../helper/formSelectOptions";

export default function AddClientField() {
  return (
    <>
      <TextField
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
        id="firstName"
        label="First Name"
        name="firstName"
        autoFocus
      />
      <TextField
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
        id="lastName"
        label="Last Name"
        name="lastName"
      />
      <TextField
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
        id="email"
        label="Email Address"
        name="email"
      />
      <TextField
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
        id="phone"
        label="Phone Number"
        name="phone"
      />
      <TextField
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
        id="address"
        label="Address"
        name="address"
      />
      <TextField
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
        select
        id="citizenship"
        label="Citizenship"
        name="citizenship"
        defaultValue="U.S. Citizen"
      >
        {citizenship.map((option) => (
          <MenuItem key={option.value} value={option.value}>
            {option.label}
          </MenuItem>
        ))}
      </TextField>
      <TextField
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
        select
        id="medicaid"
        label="Medicaid Eligibility"
        name="medicaid"
        defaultValue={true}
      >
        <MenuItem value={true}>Yes</MenuItem>
        <MenuItem value={false}>No</MenuItem>
      </TextField>
      <TextField
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
        select
        id="daycare"
        label="Daycare Eligibility"
        name="daycare"
        defaultValue={true}
      >
        <MenuItem value={true}>Yes</MenuItem>
        <MenuItem value={false}>No</MenuItem>
      </TextField>
      <TextField
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
        select
        id="status"
        label="Status"
        name="status"
        defaultValue="1"
      >
        {status.map((option) => (
          <MenuItem key={option.value} value={option.value}>
            {option.label}
          </MenuItem>
        ))}
      </TextField>
      <TextField
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
        select
        id="channel"
        label="How did you hear about us?"
        name="channel"
        defaultValue="1"
      >
        {channels.map((option) => (
          <MenuItem key={option.value} value={option.value}>
            {option.label}
          </MenuItem>
        ))}
      </TextField>
      <TextField
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
        id="physician"
        label="Physician"
        name="physician"
      />
      <TextField
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
        id="diagnosis"
        label="Diagnosis"
        name="diagnosis"
      />
      <TextField margin="normal" fullWidth id="note" label="Note" name="note" />
      <TextField
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
        select
        id="isEnrolled"
        label="Is Enrolled?"
        name="isEnrolled"
        defaultValue={false}
        sx={{ marginBottom: 5 }}
      >
        <MenuItem value={true}>Yes</MenuItem>
        <MenuItem value={false}>No</MenuItem>
      </TextField>
    </>
  );
}
